itunes:summary:
Derek Weida and producer Owen sit down for another episode and discuss anything and everything supplements. He explains why training, nutrition and supplements are the trifecta of fitness: They are all equally as important to a built lean physique. The world of supplements is severely oversaturated and confusing but Derek is here to help you figure out what exactly you need.
